               <p>London Cases, before Mr. Recorder.</p>


               <p>180. 
               
                  <persName id="t18230115-9-defend153" type="defendantName">
                     ROBERT 
                     HALE
                  <interp inst="t18230115-9-defend153" type="surname" value="HALE"></interp>
